comment.text: This text displays a label indicating the logo is intended for a specific diagram viewer. It appears within a settings section, likely on a white-labeling page, and includes the logo's dimensions. Translators should ensure the term "diagram viewer" is accurately translated for consistency with other UI elements.

usage.context:
<Text
 fontSize="15px"
 fontWeight="600"
 className="settings_unavailable"
 >
 {t("LogoForViewer", { diagramViewer: t("Common:DiagramViewer") })} (
 {logoUrls[15].size.width}x{logoUrls[15].size.height})
 </Text>
 <div className="logos-wrapper">
 <Logo
 name={logoUrls[15].name}
